{"title":"Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #16: Condor Acciaio","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-condor-acciaio","date":1742323182000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-condor-acciaio\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #16: Condor Acciaio</a></p>\n\n<p>Whether you’re looking for a new bike or just want to try out some of the world’s best, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days</a> offer a unique experience to test the latest top-end bikes from the leading brands on the market. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next up in our run-through of some of the incredible bikes that you can test ride at this years Track Days is the Condor Acciaio.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Acciaio is the London brand’s steel endurance road bike, made with <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/voyage-of-columbus-inside-the-italian-steel-giant\">Columbus</a> Spirit and Max tubes, with a carbon fork. Being an endurance bike it’s all about comfort on the rides and has clearance for 35mm tyres. Framesets are priced at £1,399.99 and full bikes start from £2,410.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Condor Acciaio will be at the following Track Days events:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>26<sup>th</sup> April 2025, Odd Down Cycle Track Bath,<br />17<sup>th</sup> May 2025, Lee Valley VeloPark London,<br />7<sup>th</sup> June 2025, The Brownlee Centre, Leeds</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information on Cyclist Track Days click <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/cc/cyclist-track-days-2025-3855053\" target=\"_blank\">BOOK YOUR TICKET HERE</a></strong></h3>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      